      "content": "thanks. i see what u mean. i've had some people in my comments lately saying that these kinds of programs are actually polarizing or that they focus too much on identity rather than just being a good business. how do i address that without getting into a huge political debate? should i acknowledge that there are different views on it or just stick to what we're doing?",
